      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 12,
      "message": "It's not wrong actually. According to documentation for targetPort field - \"If this is not specified, the value of the 'port' field is used (an identity map).  https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/generated/kubernetes-api/v1.10/#serviceport-v1-core",
